profile:
We offer professional window cleaning service for seasonal and contract jobs!

Whether it a house, apartment, condo or an industrial or commercial business – CTHRU Window Cleaning is ready to provide top quality window cleaning services!

At CTHRU Window Cleaning, we want your cleaning experience to be as easy and rewarding as possible. Whether you’re looking for a one time clean or recurring appointments, call us today for a free estimate!

Who are we?  You sure you want to know? If somebody told you we were your average ordinary window cleaners...somebody lied.
​
CTHRU is a Toronto/Durham based window and eavestrough cleaning service founded by two cousins who decided to put their combined years of experience into action with their own business.
 
Lets face it, window cleaning is a luxury service and CTHRU is committed to providing that luxury to you in every way. We offer professional window and gutter cleaning services for seasonal and contract jobs!
Whether it's a house, apartment, condo or an industrial or commercial business – CTHRU is ready to provide top quality service!
 
CTHRU has made it’s main endeavour to create long term, reliable, happy relationships with customers by consistently delivering excellent service. With over 8 Years of professional experience, we guarantee your full satisfaction.
 
We specialize in residential window and eavestrough cleaning in the Toronto and Durham area. Your home is your castle, and deserves to be treated as such. At CTHRU Window Cleaning, we want your cleaning experience to be as easy and rewarding as possible. Whether you’re looking for a one time clean or recurring appointments, call us today for a free estimate!
​
If you still are not sure about us, feel free to check out our stellar reviews from the valued clients we've worked with in the past by clicking the link below. Hope to hear from you!

Residential / Commercial Window & Gutter Cleaning Services in the GTA

With over 15 years + experience, Jessie's Spotless Window Cleaning Services provides unmatched window & gutter cleaning services through fully qualified trained window cleaners and site supervisors.

We make sure that the home owners, building managers, and supervisors are left with a lasting impression based on our service. profile:
Hi there and welcome to my page! I am a third year student, studying synthetic biology at Western University. During the summers, I run a window cleaning business with College Pro. This is my own small business, and my whole team consists of students, like me. Our goal is to provide you quick and efficient service and with a level of quality and customer service which you have never seen before.

We service residential homes doing interior and exterior window cleaning, eavestrough cleaning, siding cleaning, and even concrete and deck powerwashing and sealing. We would love to have the opportunity to do some work for you this summer, so please don't hesitate to reach out for a free, no obligation quote, or to chat if you have any questions or inquiries! 

We look forward to meeting you!
